      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong finish, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features functioning as intended. It offers a reliable driving experience for anyone looking for a solid, dependable car that has been treated with care.",
